		"description": "<p>At 1st level, your medical training helps you save lives and promote health. You gain proficiency with the Medicine skill, and you gain an expertise die on Medicine checks. For you, expertise dice on Medicine checks can be upgraded from d8 to d12, exceeding the usual limit on expertise dice.</p>\n<p>Also, whenever you stabilize a creature, and whenever you use an item to remove poison, disease, or ongoing damage from a creature, that creature regains hit points equal to your proficiency modifier.</p>",
